  "detailed_description": "<h1>About the Demo</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demo contains everything from the main game except the save/load functionality. Try it )</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Several years ago the world lost to the Dark Lord in final battle. So he chewed away most of the world dimension, leaving only 2 behind. Everything was destroyed, and even the Death does not show up any more. Besides that, the world is still livable. Get a job. Become a citizen. Invest into local economy. Travel to distant lands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to pick up your first monster:</strong></h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/1420a306e6ffa744c5ac5d6ddf3d67b6.poster.avif?t=1755315957\" width=614 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/1420a306e6ffa744c5ac5d6ddf3d67b6.webm?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/1420a306e6ffa744c5ac5d6ddf3d67b6.mp4?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Approach them from behind. <br></li><li>Press action key (default is \"E\")<br></li><li>Press \"E\" again to throw monster.</li></ul>Note: if you carry anything in your hands, you can't climb ladders.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to get a job if you don't have a citizenship yet:</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/03611bf0751ef07dba1a9853912045f8.poster.avif?t=1755315957\" width=614 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/03611bf0751ef07dba1a9853912045f8.webm?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/03611bf0751ef07dba1a9853912045f8.mp4?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ask locals, they might have daily jobs for you. Press \"E\" to talk.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to build custom pathway:</strong> </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/847f08b9b35db02b004dbaea421ba830.poster.avif?t=1755315957\" width=614 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/847f08b9b35db02b004dbaea421ba830.webm?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687130/extras/847f08b9b35db02b004dbaea421ba830.mp4?t=1755315957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use crates, movable teleports, and other objects.",
